in both Batch A and Bath B to please honour Osun Government. No sacrifice is too much for the future of our students. “May Osun continue to move forward”. Vanguard A delegation from the Federal Government’s Social Investment Programme, N-POWER, Friday, paid a commendation visit to volunteers who organised remedial summer classes for pupils in SSS1 to SSS3 in Ilesa East Local Government area of the state of Osun. August 25, 2017 In "News" DR. Vannavar Bush was the man who developed the early technology of what has come down to our age as the computer. But he didn’t see long enough to capture the far-range reach of his work. He didn’t even see up to 20 years of the limitless possibilities of the… June 19, 2012 In "Viewpoint" "We have been asked to buy textbooks so as to prepare for the coming Senior WAEC but most of us have not been able to do that because of unavailability of money. Many of us cannot afford the textbooks and have been wondering how to pass the fast approaching exams." December 18, 2017 In "News"